Lunarpine heard his comm chirp, He figured Prowl'd be around. "Prowl 
have you heard anything from Shadow Wing?"(hey that rhymes) 

Prowls response didn't come as any surprise. She didn't log out, she 
hasn't called in, the two possibilities went through his head again 
and again he feared the worse.

"I need you're help. Shadow Wings gone off on her own, I need your 
eyes in the air, and if possible,Strikers nose on the ground. If we 
can track her then the pussycons can too, I'm awaiting your response."

Lunarpine stopped at the top of a hill smelling the air. she'd done 
well to hide her scent. He was beginning to wonder if she was trying 
to not be followed, or found.

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Prowl/Kluster::
> 
> Prowl frowns, thinking over what Arcangel said.
> 
> "We fix the Ark, and then we do something else," he says to 
Arcangel, 
> begining his decent toward the Ark when a transmission stops him.
> 
> "Prowl," Kluster's voice says over the comm-link, "Lunarpine commed 
in. He 
> was babbling about something about you contacting him and that 
you're an owl."
> 
> Prowl frowns. "I'll contact him," he says.
> 
> "Lunarpine," he says into his comm-link, "This is Prowl, you wanted 
to talk 
> to me?"
